nexml.meta:
The matrix in Zhu et al. (1999) expanded the matrix of Cloutier and Ahlberg (1996). From methods:
We added Psarolepis and three non-osteichthyan taxa (Acanthodes, an acanthodian, Ctenacanthus, a chondrichthyan, and Dicksonosteus, a placoderm) to the 33 taxa in ref. 14 [Cloutier and Ahlberg 1996]. We also added 9 characters to the 140 characters in ref. 14 to reflect the variations found in Psarolepis and the three non-osteichthyan outgroups.
[Cloutier, R. and Ahlberg, PE in Interrelationships of fishes (eds Stiassny, Parenti, and Johnson) 445-480 (Academic, New York, 1996).]
